      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Song For Peter</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>On the 27th of august 2010</l>
          <l>I’ve made a promise to a special old man</l>
          <l>On exactly 6:20 pm</l>
          <l>I said “from now on I'd be a better man”</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>And he told me what he's been thru</l>
          <l>Where he slept</l>
          <l>What he had to do to get a piece of bread</l>
          <l>Looking back he drops a tear,</l>
          <l>That rough war he calls a sin</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>And it's green, green all around</l>
          <l>On this land I remember it all</l>
          <l>And it's green, green all around</l>
          <l>From now on I'm a better man</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>He said: “be good to your mother</l>
          <l>Help your father</l>
          <l>Do what I could not do, be true</l>
          <l>Be proud of who you are</l>
          <l>Make a stand</l>
          <l>Tell everyone you know what I can't forget”</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
